- $P(X=8) = \binom{10}{8}(0.7)^8(0.3)^2 = 45 \times 0.5764801 \times 0.09 = 0.2334812890$
- $P(X=9) = \binom{10}{9}(0.7)^9(0.3)^1 = 10 \times 0.4035361 \times 0.3 = 0.1210608300$
- $P(X=10) = \binom{10}{10}(0.7)^{10} = 0.0282475249$

