- $i=8$: $0.000025$
- $i=9$: $-0.0000028$
- $i=10$: $0.00000028$
- $i=11$: $-0.000000025$
- $i=12$: $0.0000000021$

Sum $\approx 0.367857$

Therefore:
$$D_{12} = 12! \times 0.367857 = 479001600 \times 0.367857 \approx 176214841$$

The probability of no matches:
$$P(\text{no matches}) = \frac{176214841}{12^{12}} = \frac{176214841}{8916100448256} \approx 0.019763$$

The probability of at least one match:
$$P(\text{at least one match}) = 1 - 0.019763 \approx 0.980237$$

Rounding to a reasonable number of significant figures (4-5):

